body:
what is this nonsense where riot forces you to type out &#039;&#039;I Agree&#039;&#039; not to leave games anymore?

''Going AFK or abandoning a match (even if it's unintentional) isn't cool. 
it wastes everyone's time, hurts your teammates, and you'll face harsher penalties if it keeps happening.
So, help us out: can you agree to not leave any further games?''

this is inconsiderate and legally wrong, anyhow i will HOLD riot to account for anything that happens because they try to force me to keep playing no matter what, because its &#039;&#039;not cool&#039;&#039; {{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} 

burgler breaks in while playing league: HEY! the silver cutlery is that way hurry up!, you are distracting me! {{sticker:sg-ahri-3}} 
psychopathic homocidal maniac looking through the window while you&#039;re playing league .-.: lets him in and tells him he can be psychotic after league! {{sticker:sg-syndra}} 
house is on fire: takes laptop with outside to continue playing while roasting marshmallows! {{sticker:sg-jinx}} 
what its a pc? asks neighbours to put out the fire with extinquisher while playing?? XD works in the sims O,O
earthquake happens~: keeps playing in awkward positions! just &#039;&#039;shaking&#039;&#039; it off ~.~ (nice practice) {{sticker:sg-kiko}} 
tsunami: continues playing on surfboard! {{sticker:sg-miss-fortune}}
car drives through your wall: pizza delivery!?????? {{sticker:sg-poppy}}
terrorist attack: you think you can hold that nade for 20 more minutes? {{sticker:sg-lux-2}}
power outage: is running pc/laptop on manual recharger! {{sticker:sg-ezreal}}
mum unplugs the cable: gets leaverbuster punishment .o. {{sticker:sg-ahri-1}}
well she never agreed did she? :/ 

how the heck can a game company hold their players responsible for this?
this system needs removal or at least that weird message O.o
riot is telling people to ignore whatever happens, and just keep playing league -.-
since when is a game more important than life?????
since when is WASTING time already wasted on a game so horrible that it requires agreeing to ignore life?,
and be 100% focused on a GAME?

so i assume riot also takes responsibility for this?
legally seen they put themselves in a bad position.

can a riot employee explain all this please?
zero empathy or tolerance, just punish those even when its not their fault?
riot created judge dredd? {{sticker:sg-janna}}

